name: Gulqiz

name: Gulg‘uncha

name: Gulhayo

name: Gulhayot

name: Go‘zalbeka, Go‘zalbika

name: Go‘zalgul

name: Go‘zaljon

name: Go‘zaloy

name: Go‘zalposhsha

name: Had’ya, Hadiya

name: Had’yaboy, Hadiyaboy

name: Had’yatulla, Hadiyatulla

name: Haydarqul

name: Hayitbek

name: Hayitberdi

name: Hayitboy
meaning: Qar. Hayit (Hayit+boy)

name: Hayitkeldi

name: Hayitmamat

name: Hayitmat

name: Hayitturdi

name: Hayitxon

name: Hamdamqul

name: Hamdo‘st

meaning: Qar. Hamza va Ali

name: Hamzamurod
meaning: Qar. Hamza va Murod

name: Hamzqul
meaning: Qar. Hamza (Hamza+qul)

name: Hamrotosh

name: Hamroxo‘ja

name: Hamrosho
meaning: Qar. Hamro va Sho(h)

name: Hamroqul

name: Hamroqo‘zi
meaning: Qar. Hamro va Qo‘zi

name: Hanafiya

name: Hanqa

name: Hasanmirza
meaning: Qar. Hasan va Mirza

name: Hasanqul

meaning: Qayg‘urib yurib, armon bilan erishilgan bola yoki onasi yosh o‘lib qolgan bola

name: Hasratqul
meaning: Qar. Hasrat (Hasrat+qul)

name: Hilla

name: Himmatqul

name: Himoyiddin
meaning: Qar. Humoyiddin

name: Hindboy, Hindiboy
meaning: Yovvosh, beozor, muloyim, mo‘min-qobil bola yoki qora bola

name: Hinduboy
meaning: Qar. Hindboy

name: Hisomiddin

name: Hodimirza
meaning: Qar. Hodi va Mirza

name: Hodimuhammad

name: Hodixon

name: Hodixo‘ja

meaning: Qar. Hodi (Hodi+ya)

name: Hodiqul

name: Hodiqurbon

name: Hojiali

name: Hojiahmad

name: Hojib

name: Hojibola

name: Hojibotir

name: Hojiboqi
meaning: Qar. Hoji va Boqi

name: Hojibulla

name: Hojiburhon
meaning: Qar. Hoji va Burhon

name: Hojivali
meaning: Qar. Hoji va Vali

name: Hojidada

name: Hojiddin

name: Hojiislom
meaning: Islom dini ziyoratchisi yoki qar. Hoji va Islom

name: Hojikamol
meaning: Qar. Hoji va Kamol

name: Hojikarim
meaning: Qar. Hoji va Karim

name: Hojikeldi

name: Hojim

name: Hojimamat
meaning: Qar. Hojimuhammad

name: Hojimat
meaning: Qar. Hojimuhammad

name: Hojimirza
meaning: Qar. Hoji va Mirza

name: Hojimurod
meaning: Hoji yetkazgan orzu, maqsad; hoji ato qilgan bola

name: Hojimuhammad
meaning: Qar. Hoji va Muhammad

name: Hojimuhiddin
meaning: Qar. Hoji va Muhiddin

name: Hojinabi

name: Hojinazar

name: Hojipo‘lat

name: Hojirahim
meaning: Qar. Hoji va Rahim

name: Hojirahmat
meaning: Qar. Hoji va Rahmat

name: Hojirahmon
meaning: Qar. Hoji va Rahmon

name: Hojisalim
meaning: Qar. Hoji va Salim

name: Hojisafar
meaning: Hojilar oilasiga mansub va safar oyida tug‘ilgan bola

name: Hojisafo

name: Hojisiddiq
meaning: Qar. Hoji va Siddiq

name: Hojisoli
meaning: Qar. Hoji va Soli(h)

name: Hojiturdi

name: Hojiumar

name: Hojiusmon
meaning: Qar. Hoji va Usmon

name: Hojixol

name: Hojixon
meaning: Qar. Hoji (Hoji+xon)

name: Hojio‘roz

name: Hojiqobil
meaning: Qar. Hoji va Qobil

name: Hojiqori
meaning: Qar. Hoji va Qori

name: Hojiqosim
meaning: Qar. Hoji va Qosim

name: Hojiqul
meaning: Qar. Hoji (Hoji+qul)

name: Hojiqurbon
meaning: Qurbon oyida tug‘ilgan va hojilar oilasiga mansub bola

name: Hojiqo‘zi
meaning: Qar. Hoji va Qo‘zi

meaning: Bibliyadagi Abraam ismining arabcha shakli bo‘lib, xalqlar otasi ma’nosini anglatadi. Rivoyatlarga ko‘ra, Ibrohimning Ishoq va Ismoil degan o‘g‘gillari bolgan. Ishoqdan yahudiy xalqi, Ismoildan esa arablar tarqalgan

name: Ibrohimmirza
meaning: Qar. Ibrohim va Mirza

name: Ibrohimxalil
meaning: Ibrohim Allohning do‘stidir yoki qar. Ibrohim va Xalil

name: Ibrohimxo‘ja
meaning: Xo‘jalar avlodiga mansub Ibrohim (qar.) ismli bola

name: Ibrohimcha
meaning: Ibrohim (qar.) ismli jajji, kenja o‘g‘il

name: Ibrohimqul
meaning: Ibrohim payg‘ambarning quli, sodiq xizmatkori

name: Idi
meaning: Iyd bayram (hayit) kuni tug‘ilgan bola

name: Idibek
meaning: Hayit kuni tug‘ilgan va beklar avlodiga mansub bola

name: Idimuhammad
meaning: Hayit kuni tug‘ilgan o‘g‘ilni Muhammad (sav) o‘z panohiga olsin

name: Idris
meaning: Aynan: o‘quvchi, o‘rganuvchi, tirishqoq, bilimdon. Idris payg‘ambar o‘qishda tirishqoqligi tufayli mana shunday nom (laqab) olgan. Demak, Idris - tirishqoq, gayratli bola

name: Idrisali
meaning: Qar. Idris va Ali

name: Idrismirza
meaning: Qar. Idris va Mirza

name: Idrisxon
meaning: Qar. Idris (Idris+xon)

name: Idrisqul
meaning: Idris (as)ning quli, sodiq xizmatkori

name: Idrok
meaning: Aqlli, bilimdon, fahm-farosatli

name: Ijobat
meaning: Orzumizning, iltijomizning qabul qilishinish, amalga oshishi. Bolasiz oilalarda farzand ko‘rishsa, shunday nom berishadi

name: Ijozali
meaning: Alining mo‘jizasi, karomati

name: Izboy
meaning: Iz-kuch, qudrat yoki qadam, yohud azizlik izzatlilik; qadr-qimmat. Asli: Izbosar, Izbosti (qar.)

name: Izbos
meaning: Izbosar, Izbosdi ismlarining qisqargan shakli

name: Izbosar
meaning: Otasining yoki oldingi akalarining izini (o‘rnini) bosuvchi bola

name: Izbosdi
meaning: Otasining yoki oldingi akalarining o‘rnini bosadi, egallaydi

name: Izboskan
meaning: Otasining yoki o‘zidan oldingi farzandlarning izini (o‘rnini) bosadigan bola

name: Izzat
meaning: Hurmat, ikrom; qadr-qimmat sohibi

name: Izzatali
meaning: Alining qadr-qimmati, sharafi, izzat-ikromi yoki izzatli-ikromli odam bo‘lsin va Ali o‘z panohida asrasin

name: Izzatbek
meaning: Beklar avlodiga mansub, izzat-ikromli, e’zozli bola

name: Izzatmirza
meaning: Izzat-ikromli va o‘qimishli, bilimli yigit bo‘lsin

name: Izzatulla
meaning: Allohning kuchi, qudrati, shonu shavkati yoki Allohning hurmatli bandasi

name: Izzatxo‘ja
meaning: Xo‘jalar naslidan bo‘lgan hurmat-ehtiromga loyiq bola

name: Izzatsho
meaning: Eng mo‘tabar, eng hurmatli bola

name: Izom
meaning: Ulug‘lar, buyuklar, ya’ni ulug‘lar, aslzodalar nasliga mansub bola. Asli: Izomiddin (qar.)

name: Izomiddin
meaning: Dinning ulug‘vorligi; buyukligi; kuchi, qudrati

name: Izommirza
meaning: Qar. Izom va Mirza

name: Izomxo‘ja
meaning: Xo‘jalar naslidan bo‘lgan ulug‘, mo‘tabar bola

name: Izomqul
meaning: Qar. Izom (Izom+qul)

name: Izoh
meaning: Qar. Izohiddin

name: Izohiddin
meaning: Dinni sharhlovchi, tushuntiruvchi, talqin qiluvchi

name: Izhor
meaning: Qar. Izhoriddin

name: Izhoriddin
meaning: Dinning oshkoraligi; dinning namoyon va ravshanligi

name: Iymanjon
meaning: Iboli, uyatchan; odobli bola yoki kutib, intizor bo‘lib erishilgan bola

name: Ikmol
meaning: Kamolatga yetgan, mukammal bola

name: Ikrom
meaning: Izzat, ehtirom, obro‘, martaba yoki sovg‘a, tuhfa. Qar. Ikromiddin. Shakllari: Ikromjon, Ikromjon

name: Ikromali
meaning: Qar. Ikrom va Ali

name: Ikromiddin
meaning: Dinning yuksakligi, ulug‘vorligi, dinning mo‘tabarligi, e’zozli

name: Ikrommirza
meaning: Qar. Ikrom va Mirza

name: Ikromxo‘ja
meaning: Xo‘jalar naslidan bo‘lgan izzat-e’tiborga loyiq bola

name: Ikromcha
meaning: Izzatu e’zozli o‘g‘ilcha

name: Ilash
meaning: Otasiga (o‘zidan oldingi aka-opasiga) ergashib (ilashib) ulg‘aysin. Shakllari: Ilashboy, Ilashjon

name: Ilashqul
meaning: Qar. Ilash (Ilash+qul)

name: Ildam
meaning: Chaqqon, g‘ayratli bola

name: Ildiz
meaning: Ildizi mustahkam, umri uzoq bo‘lsin

name: Ildirim
meaning: Chaqmoq, yashun; nur, shu’la, yog‘du. Chaqqon chaqqanda tug‘ilgan bola. Sol: Yoldirim

name: Ilyos
meaning: Aynan: Mening tangrim Yeliyaxin (Yax’yo) Allohning kuchi, qudrati yoki xalqlarning sevimligi, kishilar qadrlovchi, ezozlovchi odam. Obihayot ichib Xizr kabi mangu tirik deb faraz qilinadigan payg‘ambarning nomi. Quruqda Xizr bo‘lsa, suvlikda Ilyos kishilarning madadkori, hamrohi deb hisoblanadi

name: Ilyosali
meaning: Qar. Ilyos va Ali

name: Ilyosiddin
meaning: Ilyosning dini, imoni, e’tiqodi

name: Ilyosxon
meaning: Qar. Ilyos

name: Ilyosxo‘ja
meaning: Qar. Ilyos (Ilyos+xo‘ja)

name: Ilyosqul
meaning: Ilyos payg‘ambarning quli, xizmatkori

name: Ilim
meaning: Ilimli, bilimdon. Sol: Ilimiddin. Shakllari: Ilimbek, Ilimboy, Ilimjon

name: Ilimbek
meaning: Beklar naslidan bo‘lgan, bilimli, dono bola

name: Ilimdor
meaning: Bilimdon, donishmand

name: Ilkin
meaning: To‘ng‘ich bola yoki el farzandi

name: Ilmi
meaning: Qar. Ilmiddin

name: Ilmiddin
meaning: Din ilmi, diniy ma’rifat; din ilmi bilimdoni

name: Ilmiyor
meaning: Bilimli, o‘qimishli, ilmu ma’rifat yor bo‘lsin

name: Ilmijon
meaning: Qar. Ilmi (Ilmi+jon)

name: Ilmirahim
meaning: Allohning ilmi; rahm-shafqat, muruvvat ilmi

name: Ilmirahmon
meaning: Rahmonning (qar.), ya’ni Alloh ilmi; mehru shafqat, muruvvat ilmi

name: Ilmiyazdon
meaning: Alloh ilmi; Allohning kuchi, qudrati, mo‘jizasi

name: Ilmiyat
meaning: Bilimlar sohibi, ma’rifatli, dono

name: Ilmihayot
meaning: Hayot, tiriklik ilmi; baxtu saodat ilmi

name: ilmulla
meaning: Qar. Ilimulla

name: Ilojboy
meaning: Da’vo, shifo. Asli: Ilojiddin

name: Ilojiddin
meaning: Dinning ko‘magi, yordami; dinning xaloskorligi

name: Ilohbaxsh
meaning: Allohga baxsh etgan, ato qilgan bola

name: Ilohdod
meaning: Alloh bergan, Alloh tuhfa qilgan bola

name: Ilohyor
meaning: Alloh qo‘llovchi, panohiga oluvchi bola

name: Ilg‘or
meaning: Oldinga boruvchi, yetakchi; tezkor, ildam yoki va’da, ahdu paymon

name: Ilhom
meaning: Ruhlanish, jo‘sh urish; intilish, hayoti sevish

name: Ilhomali
meaning: Qar. Ilhom va Ali

name: Ilhomiddin
meaning: Dindan ruhlanuvchi, ilhomlanuvchi

name: Ilhommirza
meaning: Qar. Ilhom va Mirza

name: Ilhomxo‘ja
meaning: Xo‘jalar naslidan bo‘lgan ruhlanib, g‘ayrati jo‘sh urib yuruvchi bola

name: Imdod
meaning: Ko‘mak, madad, yordam. Qar. Imdodulla

name: Imdodulla
meaning: Allohning ko‘magi, yordami, marhamati

name: Imin
meaning: Xavfsiz, bexatar. Qar. Emin. Shakllari: Iminjon, Imintoy, Imincha

name: Imod, Imonboy
meaning: Tayanch, suyanchiq, turgak, madad, yordam

name: Imodali
meaning: Ali ato qilgan suyanch, madad; Alining ko‘magi tufayli erishilgan bola

name: Imodiddin
meaning: Dinning tayanchi, asosi yoki dinning bosh homiysi, dinning sodiq xizmatkori

name: Imodulla
meaning: Allohning ko‘magi, iltifoti yoki Alloh ato qilgan tayanch, suyanch

name: Imon
meaning: Aynan: Oldinda turuvchi, peshvo; masjidda oldinda turib namozni boshqaruvchi; musulmonlarning diniy rahbari, peshvosi. Imom so‘zi Alining avlodlari hisoblanuvchi va shiitlar mazhabiga mansub kishilarning VII-X asrlardan udum bo‘lib kelgan unvonidir va u ushbu unvonga sazovor shaxsning ismiga qo‘shib aytilgan: Imom ALi kabi

name: Imomali
meaning: Ali oldinda turuvchi, rahbar, peshvodir. Muhammad (sav)ning tog‘asi shiitlarning birinchi imomi hisoblanadi. Shu sababli u Imomali deb yuritilgan va bu nom kishilar ismiga ham o‘tgan

name: Imombaxsh
meaning: Imom ato qilgan, bergan bola

name: Imombek
meaning: Beklar naslidan bo‘lgan diniy peshvo, diniy rahbar

name: Imombergan
meaning: Diniy boshliq (peshvo) ato qilgan, erishtirgan bola. Bu ism biror muqaddas qadamjoyga ziyorat qilingach tug‘ilgan bolaga beriladi

name: Imomberdi
meaning: Diniy peshvo, muqaddas avliyo ato qilgan bola

name: Imomboy
meaning: Qar. Imom (Imom+boy)

name: Imomyor
meaning: Imom (diniy peshvoning) do‘sti, hamrohi, yo‘ldoshi yoki imom hamroh, yo‘ldosh bo‘luvchi, panohiga oluvchi bola

name: Imomzoda
meaning: Imomning farzandi, o‘g‘li yoki imomlar avlodiga mansub bola

name: Imomiddin

name: Imommirza
meaning: Qar. Imom va Mirza

name: Imommurod
meaning: Imom ko‘magi tufayli erishilgan orzu yoki imom ato qilgan bola ulg‘ayib murod-maqsadiga yetsin

name: Imommuhammad
meaning: Muhammad (sav) dinning peshvosi, sardoridir

name: Imomnazar

name: Imomnafas

name: Imomniyoz

name: Imomrasul
meaning: Qar. Imom va Rasul

name: Imomsaid
meaning: Imom erishtirgan baxtli, tolei baland bola

name: Imomxol
meaning: Dinning xolli peshvosi, boshlig‘i

name: Imomxo‘ja
meaning: Xo‘jalar avlodiga mansub bo‘lgan din peshvosi

name: Imomcha
meaning: Madrasa talabasi, kelgusida imom bo‘luvchi bola yoki imomlarning kichigi, kenjasi

name: Imomqul
meaning: Din peshvosi (imom)ning quli, imomga sodiq bola

name: Imom
meaning: Ishonch, e’tiqod, ishonish, sig‘inish. Imom Islom dinining asosiy shartlaridan biri bo‘lib, bunda Allohga, islom dini va Muhammadga ishonch, etiqod ko‘zda tutiladi. Demak, imon, etiqodli bola. Shakllari: Imonbek, Imonboy, Imonjon

name: Imonali
meaning: Aliga e’tiqod qiluvchi, sig‘inuvchi bola yoki imon-etiqodli bolani Ali o‘z panohida asrasin

name: Imonberdi
meaning: Alloh bergan imon-e’tiqodli bola

name: Imonkeldi
meaning: Imon-e’tiqodli tilladek aziz, bebaho bola

name: Imontilla
meaning: Dinga e’tiqodli tilladek aziz, bebaho bola

name: Imonqul
meaning: Qar. Imon (Imon+qul)

name: Imron
meaning: Tiriklik, barhayotlik, uzoq umr ko‘ruvchi

name: Imroh
meaning: Do‘stlik, birodarlik, o‘rtoqlik

name: Imtiyoz
meaning: o‘zgalardan sarbaland, farqli (imtiyozli) qilib berilgan bola

name: Imyamin
meaning: Qar. Ibniyamin

name: Inar
meaning: Inar (tuyaning bir xol zoti) kabi kuchli, qudratli bola

name: Inarkeldi
meaning: Inar (qar.) dek kuchli, baquvvat bola tug‘ildo

name: Inimcha
meaning: Ukacha, inicha; oldingi bolalarga ukacha bo‘lib yursin

name: Inkor
meaning: Tavqa qiluvchi, Allohi taolo yo‘liga o‘tuvchi bola. Shakli: Inkorbek, Inkorboy

name: Inob
meaning: Inobat, Inobiddin (qar.) ismlarining eq.shakllari: Inobboy, Inobjon, Inobxon

name: Inobiddin
meaning: Dinning marhamati, himmati, inobati

name: Inod
meaning: o‘jar, qaytmas, sarkash bola

name: Inol
meaning: Hokim, hukmron, podshoh yoki yalinib, yolg‘orib erishilgan bola

name: Inon, Inonjon
meaning: Umid qilish, ishonish, inonish, ya’ni bola yashab ketadi deb umid qilinadi

name: Inonch
meaning: Ishonish, umidlanish, ya’ni bolaning yashab ketishiga umid bog‘lash

name: Inoyat
meaning: Xayrixohlik, ko‘mak, ehson, iltifot. Asli: Inoyatulla (qar.)

name: Inoyatali
meaning: Alining himmati, ehsoni, ko‘magi

name: Inoyatrasul
meaning: Payg‘ambarning lutfu karami, ko‘magi bilan erishilgan bola

name: Inoyatulla
meaning: Allohning marhamati, lutfu karami yoki Allohning fikri, yodi. Ushbu nom Muhammad (sav)ning sifati (laqab)laridan biri bo‘lgan

name: Inoyatqul
meaning: Qar. Inoyat (Inoyat+qul)

name: Inoq
meaning: Do‘st, o‘rtoq, yo‘ldosh yoki o‘ziga mustaqil bolgan shaxs. Buxoro xonligida eng yuqori mansablardan biri ham inoq deb yuritiladi

name: Inoqmirza
meaning: Qar. Inoq va Mirza

name: Inog‘om
meaning: In’om, sovg‘a, tuhfa, hadya

name: Inson
meaning: Odam, kishi; odamshavanda bola

name: Insof, Insofboy
meaning: Pokiza, adolatli. Shakllari: Insofboy, Insofjon

name: Insofali
meaning: Pokiza, adolatpesha bolani Ali o‘z panohida asrasin

name: Insofiddin
meaning: Dinning insofli, sabr-qanoatli farzandi

name: Intizom
meaning: Tartibli, sarishta, odobli

name: Intizor
meaning: Intiq bo‘lib, orziqib kutilgan

name: Intiq, Intiqjon
meaning: Orziqib, intiq bo‘lib kutilgan

name: Intiqom
meaning: Oldingi vafot etrgan farzandlar evaziga berilgan bola

name: In’om
meaning: Tuhfa, tortiq qilib berilgan. Shakllari: In’omboy, Inomjon

name: In’omali
meaning: Alining sovg‘asi, tuhfasi

name: In’omiddin
meaning: Dinning tuhfasi, sovg‘asi; tortig‘i

name: In’ommirza
meaning: Qar. In’om va Mirza

name: In’omulla
meaning: Allohning tuhfasi, ehsoni

name: In’ommuhammad
meaning: Muhammad (sav)ning tuhfasi, ehsoni, marhamati

name: In’omnazar
meaning: Alloh e’tibor, muruvvat qilib bergan sovg‘a, ehson

name: In’omto‘ra
meaning: Alloh sovg‘a, tuhfa qilib bergan bola baland martabali bo‘lsin

name: In’omxon
meaning: Qar. In’om (Inom+xon)

name: In’omqul
meaning: Qar. In’om (Inom+qul)

name: Inqilob
meaning: Aynan: o‘zgarish, to‘ntarish. Inqilob farzandi. Yangi davrda paydo bo‘lgan ism

name: Iris, Irisboy
meaning: Iris- nasibali, farovon, baxtiyor yoki ota-onasining nasibasi, omadi bo‘lgan bola

name: Irisali
meaning: Nasibali, rizq-ro‘zli, omadli bolani Ali o‘z panohida asrasin

name: Irisli
meaning: Nasibali, baxtli bola. Sol: Iris

name: Irismat
meaning: Qar. Irismuhammad

name: Irismurod
meaning: Orzu qilingan nasibali bola yoki nasibasi butun bola ulg‘ayib murodu maqsadiga yetsin

name: Iristoy
meaning: Rizqu ro‘zli, nasibasi butun, omadli bola

name: Irisxo‘ja
meaning: Xo‘jalar naslidan bo‘lgan rizqu nasibasi butun bola

name: Irisqul
meaning: Qar. Iris (Iris+qul)

name: Iroq, Iroqboy
meaning: Aynan: Yiroq, ya’ni umri uzoq bo‘lsin

name: Irshod
meaning: To‘g‘ri yo‘l ko‘rsatuvchi, togri yolga undovchi boshliq, rahbar

name: Iskandar
meaning: Mard, qo‘rqmas, dovyurak, jasurlarning sardori yoki himoya qiluvchi, muhofazakor

name: Iskandarbek
meaning: Beklar avlodidan bo‘lgan bola. Iskandar (qar.)dek jasur bo‘lsin

name: Iskandarsho
meaning: Iskandar shohdek jasur, dovyurak

name: Iskandarqul
meaning: Qar. Iskandar (Iskandar+qul)

name: Islimiddin
meaning: Dinning bezagi, ko‘rki yoki dinga rivoj beruvchi, yuksaltiruvchi

name: Islom
meaning: Aynan: O‘zini Allohning ixtiyoriga topshirish itoatkor, islomga bo‘ysungan. Musulmonlar, Muhammad (sav) dinining nomi. Shakllari: Islomboy, Islombek, Islomjon

name: Islomali
meaning: Islomga itoat qiluvchi, musulmon bola Ali o‘z panohida olsin

name: Islombek
meaning: Beklar avlodidan bo‘lgan, musulmonlar diniga bo‘ysungan bola

name: Islomberdi
meaning: Alloh ato qilgan musulmon bola yoki Alloh musulmon bola ato qildi

name: Islomboqi
meaning: Musulmonlar dini (islom) abadiy, boqiydir yoki Muhammad diniga itoat qiluvchi bolaning umri uzoq bo‘lsin

name: Islomiddin
meaning: Dinga sodiq bola, xudojo‘y, zohid

name: Islommirza
meaning: Qar. Islom va Mirza

name: Islommurod
meaning: Islom erishtirgan orzu, murod yoki Allohga bo‘ysungan bola ulg‘ayib murodiga yetsin

name: Islomnur
meaning: Musulmonlar dini (islom)ning nuri, yog‘dusi; islom ato qilgan baxt, omad

name: Islomxon
meaning: Qar. Islom(Islom+xon)

name: Islomxo‘ja
meaning: Xo‘jalar naslidan bo‘lgan musulmon bola

name: Islomsho
meaning: Qar. Islom va Sho(h)

name: Islomqul
meaning: Islomning sodiq xizmatkori, quli

name: Islomg‘ozi
meaning: Islom yo‘lida kurashuvchi va g‘olib chiquvchi bola

name: Islomhoji
meaning: Qar. Islom va Hoji yoki Ka’bani ziyorat qilgan musulmon

name: Islohot
meaning: o‘zgarishm tuzatish (islohot) yillari tug‘ilgan bola

name: Isman
meaning: Ismatulla ismining qisqargan shakli. Eht.: Isfan

name: Ismanali
meaning: Qar. Isman va Ali yoki Isfanali

name: Ismandiyor
meaning: Qar. Isfandiyor

name: Ismanjon
meaning: Qar. Isfan (Isfan+jon) yoki Ismatulla

name: Istamtoy
meaning: Qar. Isfan (Isfan+toy) yoki Ismatulla

name: Ismonxo‘ja
meaning: Qar. Isfan (Isfan+xo‘ja) yoki Ismatulla

name: Ismancha
meaning: Kenja, jajji. Isfan (qar.) yoki Ismatulla

name: Ismanqul
meaning: Qar. Isman (Isman+qul) yoki Ismatulla

name: Ismat
meaning: Pokiza, ozoda, gunohsiz; taqvodor, poro. Shakllari: Ismatjon, Ismatxon

name: Ismatyor
meaning: Soflik, pokizalik; yaxshi fazilatlar hamdami

name: Ismatmirza
meaning: Qar. Ismat va Mirza

name: Ismatulla
meaning: Allohning begunoh, pokiza, yaxshi xislatlar sohibi bo‘lmish bandasi. Bu nom Muhammad (sav)ning sifati (laqabi) bo‘lgan

name: Ismatqul
meaning: Pokiza, begunoh bola. Qar. Ismat (Ismat+qul)

name: Ismoil
meaning: Aynan: Xudo eshitdi yoki Allohdan so‘rab olingan, Alloh tuhfa qilgan bola. Tavrotdagi rivoyatga ko‘ra, Ibrohim payg‘ambarning xotini Hojar Allohdan farzand so‘rab ijtijo qilgan. Shu tufayli tugilgan bolaga Ishmael (Ismoil) deb ism berishgan. Bu nom MUhammad (sav) oglining ismi ham bolgan. Shakllari: Ismoiljon, Ismoilxon

name: Ismoilxo‘ja
meaning: Qar. Ismoil va Xo‘ja

name: Ismoilsho
meaning: Qar. Ismoil va Sho(h)

name: Ismoilqul
meaning: Ismoilning quli, Ismoilga bo‘ysunuvchi

name: Iso
meaning: Allohning tuhfasi, ehsoni; lutfu karami; Allohning ko‘magi yoki Allohning yaqini. Iso-qadimiy yahudiycha Jexogua, Iisus (Xristos) nomining arabcha shaklidir

name: Isoboy
meaning: Qar. Iso (Iso+boy)

name: Isoyor
meaning: Iso (payg‘ambar) o‘z panohiga oluvchi, qo‘llovchi bola

name: Isom
meaning: Tayanch, suyanch, ya’ni ota-onasiga suyanchiq, ko‘makchi bo‘luvchi bola

name: Isomamat
meaning: Qar. Isomuhammad

name: Isomat
meaning: Qar. Isomuhammad

name: Isomiddin
meaning: Dinning tutqichi, suyanchi; dinga madad beruvchi, ko‘makdosh

name: Isomurod
meaning: Iso yetkazgan orzu, tilak, Isoning muruvvati, tuhfasi

name: Isomuhammad
meaning: Qar. Iso va Muhammad

name: Isomxon
meaning: Qar. Isom (Islom+xon)

name: Isomxo‘ja
meaning: Ota-onasining suyanchig‘i, madadkori bo‘lgan, xo‘jalar avlodiga mansub bola

name: Isonafas
meaning: Iso (payg‘ambar)ning nafasi, ko‘magi tufayli erishilgan bola yoki Iso nafasli; zukko, zehnli bola

name: Isotilla
meaning: Qar. Iso va Tilla

name: Isotoy
meaning: Iso payg‘ambar ismi berilgan aziz, suyukli bola yoki qar. Iso (Iso+toy)

name: Isoxon
meaning: Qar. Iso (Iso+xon)

name: Isoxo‘ja
meaning: Iso payg‘ambar nomi berilgan va xo‘jalar avlodiga mansub bola

name: Isoq
meaning: Qar. Is’hoq. Shakllari: Isoqjon, Isoqboy

name: Isoqali
meaning: Qar. Is’hoq va Ali

name: Isoqul
meaning: Iso (as)ning quli

name: Ispan
meaning: Ismand  -  Isfand - isiriq, hazratispand. Xalq bu o‘simlim, uning hidi kishini balo-qazodan, ko‘z tegishdan arraydi deb hisoblaydi. Shu tufayli uning chaqaloqqa ism sifatida qo‘yiladi

name: Isroil
meaning: Alloh yo‘lida kurashuvchi

name: Isrofil

name: Istad

name: Sanzor

name: Saodatali

meaning: Qar. Sarabek

name: Sarbola

name: Sariali

name: Sarimamat
meaning: Qar. Sarimuhammad

name: Sarimirza

name: Zaydi
meaning: Zayd so‘zi bilan boshlangan ismlarning eq.shakli

name: Zaydulla
meaning: Allohning in’omi, ehsoni, himmati

name: Zaylob
meaning: Qar. Zaylobiddin. Sol: Zaynab

name: Zaylobiddin
meaning: Qar. Zaynulobiddin. Sol: Zaynobiddin

name: Zaymiddin
meaning: Dinning yo‘lboshchisi, rahnamosi, din sardori

name: Zaynabiddin
meaning: Dinning go‘zalligi, diniy nafost yoki dinning ko‘rkli farzandi

name: Zaynabmirza
meaning: Qar. Zaynab va Mirza

name: Zaynabxo‘ja
meaning: Xo‘jalar naslidan bo‘lgan ko‘rkam bola

name: Zaynal
meaning: Zaynulobiddin (qar.) ismining eq.shakli

name: Zayni
meaning: Zayniddin (qar.) ismining eq.shakli

name: Zayniali
meaning: Ali ato qilgan ko‘rkam o‘g‘il yoki ko‘rkam ogilni Ali panohida asrasin

name: Zaynibashar
meaning: Kishilarning, insonlarning eng ko‘rkami, go‘zali

name: Zayniddin
meaning: Dinning ko‘rki, bezagi, diniy nafosat  yoki dinning ko‘rki bo‘luvchi bola

name: Zayniqul
meaning: Qar. Zayni (Zayni+qul)

name: Zaynulislom
meaning: Islomning bezagi, ko‘rki

name: Zaynulla
meaning: Allohning go‘zal, ko‘hlik bandasi

name: Zaynulobiddin
meaning: Dinga sig‘inuvchilar (xudojo‘ylar)ning eng a’losi, go‘zali. Bu nom imom Alining faxriy unvoni bo‘lgan va oldin shiitlar, keyinchalik esa sunniylar orasida kishi ismi sifatida tarqalgan

name: Zayriddin
meaning: Asli Zayniddin (qar.) bo‘lsa kerak. Eht.: Zohiriddin (qar.)

name: Zayfulla
meaning: Alloh yuborgan mehmon, Alloh ato qilgan bola

name: Zakariya
meaning: Zaxariya - Allohni yodda tutuvchi, Allohning xotirasi yoki er, mard, jasur

name: Zaki, Zakiboy
meaning: Qar. Zakiy, Zakiulla

name: Zakiy
meaning: Aqlli, zukko, tezfahm, sezgir, ziyrak

name: Zakiulla
meaning: Allohning sezgir, zukko bandasi yoki Allohning ozoda, pokiza bandasi

name: Zakoulla
meaning: Allohning topqirligi, zakovati, donoligi yoki Allohning aqlli, dono bandasi

name: Zalil
meaning: Tuban, past; bechora, faqir, gadoy. Ota-ona o‘zlarining farzandga muhtoj bo‘lganini shunday ifodalaydi

name: Zamzamali
meaning: Qar. Zamzam va Ali

name: Zamir
meaning: Yurak, qalb, vijdon. Asli: Zamiriddin (qar.)

name: Zamiriddin
meaning: Dinning yuragi, qalbi; dinga sodiqlik bilan vijdonan sig‘inuvchi

name: Zamon

name: Zamonali

name: Zamonberdi
meaning: Alloh davriga, zamonasiga munosib o‘g‘il ato qildi

name: Zamonbibi
meaning: Zamonasining muhtarama qizi

name: Zamonkeldi
meaning: Zamonasi, davriga munosib o‘g‘il tug‘ildi

name: Zamonmirza
meaning: Davrining o‘qimishli, martabali o‘g‘li

name: Zamonmurod
meaning: Davri, zamonasining murod-maqsadli farzandi

name: Zamontoy
meaning: Zamonasining munosib va suyukli hurmatli farzandi

name: Zamonxo‘ja
meaning: Davrining xo‘jalar nasliga mansub bo‘lgan munosib farzandi

name: Zamonqul
meaning: Davr, zamonasining munosib, sadoqatli xizmatkori bo‘lsin

name: Zamcha
meaning: Zamcha (qovun) pishganda tug‘ilgan bola

name: Zanbur
meaning: Ari, qovoqari. Bolasi turmagan oilalarda shunday ism berishadi. Eht.: Zabur (qar.)

name: Zangi
meaning: Qoracha, qora bola yoki ko‘tariluvchi, yuksaluvchi; mahkam, mustahkam

name: Zanjir, Zanjirboy
meaning: Zanjirdek mahkam, mustahkam yoki otasi, akalariga zanjirdek bog‘lanib qolsin, yashasin

name: Zanjirali
meaning: Qar. Zanjir va Ali

name: Zarasp
meaning: Oq ot egasi, chavandoz, doro

name: Zarbat, Zarbatbek
meaning: Eht.: Zarbaft, Zarbof

name: Zarbdor
meaning: Ilg‘or, peshqadam, yangi davrda ijod qilingan ism

name: Zargar
meaning: Tillo buyumlar ustasi

name: Zargarxo‘ja
meaning: Xo‘jalar naslidan bo‘lgan bola ulg‘ayib tillakor usta bo‘lsin

name: Zariddin
meaning: Dinning tillodek bebaho, a’lo bolasi; dinning sodiq xizmatkori, sodiq xudojo‘y

name: Zarirxo‘ja
meaning: Qar. Zarir va Xo‘ja

name: Zarif
meaning: Pok, toza, pokiza, nozikfahm, ziyrak; aqlli, dono. Shakllari: Zarifboy, Zarifjon

name: Zarifiddin
meaning: Dinning pokiza, zukko farzandi

name: Zarifulla
meaning: Allohning chiroyli yoki aql-zakovatli bandasi

name: Zarifxo‘ja
meaning: Xo‘jalar naslidan bo‘lgan pokiza yoki zukko bola

name: Zarifqul
meaning: Qar. Zarif (Zarif+Qul)

name: Zarifkeldi
meaning: Qimmatli, qadrli o‘g‘il tug‘ildi

name: Zarmamat
meaning: Qar. Zarmuhammad

name: Zarqalam
meaning: Qizil qalam, tilla qalam

name: Zarqora
meaning: Zardek qimmatli va jasur, qudratli bola

name: Zarqori
meaning: Qar. Zar va Qori

name: Zarqul
meaning: Allohning qadrli, e’zozli bandasi, quli

name: Zarg‘am
meaning: Zirg‘am-arslon, sher; jasur, qo‘rqmas, dovyurak

name: Zafar
meaning: g‘olib, muzaffar; baxtli, saodatli. Shakllari: Zafarbek, Zafarjon

name: Zafariddin
meaning: Dinning zafari, g‘olibligi; dinning iqboli, istiqboli

name: Zafaroy
meaning: g‘olib, yengilmas va oydek ko‘rkam qiz

name: Za’faron
meaning: Za’faron guldek ko‘rkam yoki yoqut toshdek qimmatli, nurli

name: Zafarxo‘ja
meaning: Xo‘jalar naslidan bo‘lgan baxtli, toleli baland bola

name: Zafir
meaning: g‘olib keluvchi, yenguvchi

name: Zahiriddin
meaning: Nurli, ravshan, chehrasidan nur yog‘iluvchi yoki dinning posboni, himoyachisi

name: Zahirulla
meaning: Allohning nuri, yog‘dusi yoki Allohning panohida bo‘lgan bola

name: Zahob,  Zahab
meaning: Tilladek bebaho, qadrli (oltin)

name: Ziyo
meaning: Nurli, ravshan, yorqin yoki baxtli, tolei baland yoki ziyo so‘zi bilan boshlanadigan qo‘shma ismlar (Ziyobuddin, Ziyoali, Ziyodulla) eq.shakli

name: Ziyoahmad

name: Ziyoali

name: Ziyovuddin

name: Ziyod

name: Ziyodatulla

name: Ziyodulla
meaning: Alloh bergan ehson, tuhfa. Alloh umrini uzoq qilib bergan bola

name: Ziyodxol
meaning: Uzoq umrli hamda xosiyatli xol bilan tug‘ilgan bola

name: Ziyodqo‘zi
meaning: Qar. Ziyod va Qo‘zi

name: Ziyoviddin
meaning: Qar. Ziyovuddin

name: Ziyom, Ziyomboy
meaning: Qar. Ziyomiddin

name: Ziyomat
meaning: Qar. Ziyomuhammad

name: Ziyomiddin
meaning: Dinning boyligi, davlati yoki dinning boy, badavlat kishisi

name: Ziyomxo‘ja
meaning: Xo‘jalar avlodidan bo‘lgan, boy, badavlat bola

name: Ziyor

name: Ziyorat
meaning: Muqaddas joylarga sig‘inib, ziyorat qilib erishilgan bola

name: Ziyoriddin, Ziyoratdin
meaning: Dinga amal qiluvchi, sig‘inuvchi; hoji

name: Ziyouddin
meaning: Dinning nuri, mash’ali. Bu nom o‘rta asrlarda bazi hukmron va ruhoniylarning faxriy laqabi bo‘lgan. Sol: Ziyovuddin

name: Ziyoxo‘ja
meaning: Xo‘jalar naslidan bo‘lgan nurli, baxtu iqbolli bola

name: Ziyoqul
meaning: Qar. Ziyo (Ziyo+qul)

name: Ziyoqo‘zi
meaning: Qar. Ziyo va Qo‘zi

name: Ziyohiddin
meaning: Eht.: Ziyovuddin (qar.)

name: Ziynat
meaning: Bezangan, orolangan go‘zal, chiroyli. Shakllari: Ziynatbu, Ziynatoy, Ziynatxon

name: Zynatulla
meaning: Allohning chiroyli, yaxshi bandasi; Allohning yaxshi xislatlarga ega kishisi

name: Zikir

name: Zikirali
meaning: Alini yodga oluvchi, xotirlovchi yoki xudojo‘y bolani Ali o‘z panohida asrasin

name: Zikriyo,  Zikiriyo
meaning: Allohni eslovchi, xotirlovchi, ulug‘lovchi; darvesh, qalandar

name: Zikriyoqul
meaning: Allohni xotirlovchi, Alloh yodi bilan yashovchi

name: Zikrilla
meaning: Allohning yodi, xotirasi; Allohni eslovchi, yoz etuvchi kishi; xudojo‘y

name: Zilolboy
meaning: Pokiza, halol bola yoki muhofaza qilingan, himoyalangan bola

name: Zilulla
meaning: Allohningsoyasi, ko‘lankasi. Bu nom o‘tmishda musulmon hukmdorlarining o‘ziga xol laqabi bo‘lgan

name: Zinda
meaning: Jonli, tirik, o‘lmgan, barhayot. Asli: Shohizinda (qar.)

name: Zindaali
meaning: Ali tirik, barhayotdir yoki o‘lmaydigan, umri uzoq bolan Ali o‘z panohiga olsin

name: Zindadil
meaning: Xushchaqchaq, quvnoq, doimo shodon

name: Zinnat
meaning: Ziynatlangan, zebu ziynatlarga burkangan; go‘zal, kelishgan. Sol: Ziynat

name: Zinnatjon
meaning: Qar. Zinnat (Zinnat+jon)

name: Zinnatulla
meaning: Allohning ko‘rkam, bezangan kishisi yoki Allohga munosib, uning ko‘rkam, suyukli bandasi

name: Zinnatxo‘ja
meaning: Xo‘jalar naslidan bo‘lgan chiroyli yigit

name: Zinnatsho
meaning: Go‘zal yigitlar sardori, sultoni

name: Zobir

name: Zobirulla
meaning: Alloh asraydigan, Allohning panohida bo‘lgan bola yoki Allohning qudratli, irodali bandasi

name: Zobit, Zobitjon
meaning: Zabt etuvchi, boshqaruvchi; hokim hukmdor yoki xushyor, sergak bola

name: Zovur, Zovurboy

name: Zoid
meaning: Ustuvor, buyuk, yuksak turuvchi yoki umri ziyoda, uzun bo‘lsin. Eht.: Zohid (qar.)

name: Zoim
meaning: Boshliq, rahbar, yo‘lboshchi yoki oiladagi birinchi, bosh bola

name: Zoir,  Zoyir
meaning: Ziyoratchi, muqaddas (ilohiy) joylarga sig‘inuvchi. Eht.: Zohir (qar.) ismining o‘zgargan shakli

name: Zokir
meaning: Yodga oluvchi, eslovchi, xotirlovchi, ya’ni Allohga sig‘inuvchi. Asli: Zokirulla (qar.) Shakllari: Zokirboy, Zokirjon, Zokirxon

name: Zokiriyo
meaning: Allohni yodga oluvchi, uning zikri (yodi) bilan yashovchi bola

name: Zokiriddin
meaning: Dinni madh qiluvchi, dinning yodi bilan yashovchi; xudojo‘y bola

name: Zokirmat
meaning: Qar. Zokirmuhammad

name: Zokirmuhammad
meaning: Muhammad (sav)ni yod etuvchi, eslovchi bola yoki xudojo‘y o‘g‘ilni Muhammad (sav) o‘z panohida asrasin

name: Zokirulla
meaning: Allohni eslovchi, uni madh qiluvchi bola

name: Zokirxo‘ja
meaning: Xo‘jalar naslidan bo‘lgan xudojo‘y, dindor bola

name: Zol

name: Zomir
meaning: Nayza sanchuvchi, nayzaboz, qilichboz

name: Zorboy
meaning: Zor bo‘lib, qumsab yurib, erishilgan bola. Eht.: Zarboy (qar.)

name: Zorliq
meaning: Farzandga muhtoj bo‘lib yurib tilab olingan o‘g‘il

name: Zorman
meaning: Zormand (muhtoj) bo‘lib erishilgan farzand yoki Zormuhammad (qar.) ismining eq.shakli

name: Zormamat
meaning: Qar. Zormuhammad

name: Zormuhammad
meaning: Zorlanib, tilab olingan bolani Muhammad (sav) o‘z panohiga olsin

name: Zohid

name: Zohiddin
meaning: Dining haqiqiy, sodiq muxlisi; avliyo, taqvodor

name: Zohidnur
meaning: Muqaddas, ezgu, nur; Allohning mehri, muruvvati

name: Zohidulla
meaning: Allohning taqvodor, dindor kishisi

name: Zohir
meaning: Nurli, ravshan, yorqin yoki ko‘makchi, yordamchi, madadkor. Bu nom Muhammad (sav) sifati (laqabi) bo‘lgan

name: Zohirbek
meaning: Beklar naslidan bo‘lgan ko‘kamdosh va saodatmand bola

name: Zohiriddin
meaning: Dinning ko‘makchisi, yordamchisi, din homiysi. Sol: Zahiriddin

name: Zohiriy
meaning: Ravshan, ochiq-oydin bo‘lib turuvchi

name: Zohirmirza
meaning: Nurli, ochiq chehrali va o‘qimishli, martabali bola

name: Zohirulla

name: Zohirxo‘ja
meaning: Xo‘jalar avlodiga mansub, baxtli, iqbolli bola

name: Zubay
meaning: Zubayd (qar.) ismining eq. shakli. Shakllari: Zubaytoy, Zubayjon, Zubayxon

name: Zubayberdi
meaning: Alloh bergan tuhfa, sovg‘a

name: Zubayd
meaning: Saralangan, tanlangan, odamlarning eng yaxshisi yoki sovg‘a, tuhfa. Asli: Zubaydulla (qar.)

name: Zubaydulla
meaning: Allohning eng yaxshi ko‘rgan, tanlangan bandasi. Allohning marhamati, muruvvati, tuhfasi. Bu nom o‘rta asrda musulmonlar tomonidan Muhammad (sav)ga berilgan laqab-sifatidir

name: Zubayr
meaning: Kuchli, qudratli, aqlli, dono

name: Zubayqul
meaning: Qar. Zubayr (Zubayr+qul)

name: Zuljalol
meaning: Buyuk martaba, sharaf egasi

name: Zulkabir
meaning: Salobatli, kelishgan

name: Zulpan, Zulfan
meaning: Bilimdon, donishmand

name: Zulfali
meaning: Alining sochi; Alining qudrati

name: Zulfibek
meaning: Beklar naslidan bo‘lgan jingalak sochli bola. Asli: Zulfiddin, Zulfiqor (qar.)

name: Zulfiddin
meaning: Dinning jingalak sochli, xudojo‘y farzandi

name: Zulfinor
meaning: Jingalak sochli va qizil xol (nor) bilan tug‘ilgan bola

name: Zulfitilla
meaning: Tilla sochli, jingalak, chiroyli sochli bola

name: Zulfiqor
meaning: Aynan: Teshib o‘tuvchi, harob qiluvchi; xalifa Alining ikki damli, afsonaviy qilichining nomi; o‘tkir, keskir, kuchli, qudratli

name: Zulfihaydar
meaning: Qar. Zulfi va Haydar

name: Zulfulla
meaning: Allohning jingalak sochli farzandi

name: Zulxayr
meaning: Mehr; muruvvat; xayru sahovat egasi

name: Zulxidja
meaning: Qar. Zulhijja

name: Zulqadar
meaning: Baxtli, saodatli, baxtiyor

name: Zulqaynar, Zulqarnayn
meaning: Aynan: Qo‘sh muguzli. Bu nom makedoniyalik Iskandarning laqabi bo‘lgan yoki ikki shohli toj kiygan, ya’ni g‘arb va Sharq hukmdori

name: Zunnor
meaning: Jundan to‘qilgan dagal belbog‘cham ip, ya’ni zunnor kabi mahkam, mustahkam bo‘lsin

name: Zunnun
meaning: Aynan: ulkan baliq egasi. Aqidaga ko‘ra Yunus payg‘ambar uch kun ulkan baliq (kit)ning ichida yashagan. Shu sabab unga ushbu laqab berilgan va keyinchalik bu nom kishilar ismiga aylangan

name: Zunnunxo‘ja
meaning: Qar. Zunnun (Zunnun+xo‘ja)

name: Zufar, Zufardeb
meaning: g‘olib, muzaffar, yengilmas; yo‘lboshchi, sarkor

name: Zufarxon
meaning: Qar. Zufar (Zufar+xon)

name: Zufarxo‘ja
meaning: Xo‘jalar naslidan bo‘lgan qudratli, g‘olib bola

name: Zuhriddin, Zuhuriddin
meaning: Dinning g‘olibligi yoki dinning g‘olib kishisi

name: Zuhrobibi
meaning: Qar. Zuhro va Bibi

name: Zuhrulla,  Zuhurulla
meaning: Allohning aniq namoyon bo‘lishi; Alloh qudratining nayomon bo‘lishi

name: Zuhur
meaning: Paydo bo‘lish, yuzaga kelish. Asli: Zuhurulla, Zuhridddin. Shakllari: Zuhurboy, Zuhurjon

name: Zo‘rali
meaning: Qar. Zo‘r va Ali yoki kuchli, qudratli o‘g‘ilni Ali qo‘llab yursin

name: Zo‘rboy
meaning: Kuchli, qudratli, g‘olib, muzaffas

name: Zo‘rmat
meaning: Qar. Zo‘rmuhammad

name: Zo‘rmuhammad
meaning: Kuchli, qudratli bo‘lib o‘ssin va Muhammad (sav) o‘z panohida asrasin yoki Muhammad (sav)ning qudrati, irodasi bo‘lgan bola

name: Zo‘rxo‘ja
meaning: Xo‘jalar avlodidan bo‘lgan bola qudratli, jasur bo‘lib yursin

name: Zo‘rqul
meaning: Allohning kuchli, jasur bandasi yoki qar. Zo‘rboy

name: Zabaroy
meaning: Baland martabali, oliynasab qiz

name: Zabarjad
meaning: Asl, qimmatbaho tosh zabarjaddek bebaho, qadrli qiz

name: Zabarmaro
meaning: Mashhur, atoqli, tengsiz, mislsiz

name: Zabiba
meaning: Mayizdek shirin, dilxoh qiz

name: Zabida
meaning: Bezangan, go‘zal, chiroyli

name: Zabira
meaning: Qar. Zabir (Zabir+a)

name: Zabiha
meaning: Alloh yo‘liga qurbonlik qiluvchi qiz yoki Alloh yo‘liga baxshida qilingan qiz

name: Zabonbibi
meaning: Biyron tilli, notiqa qiz yoki yolqinli, otashli qiz

name: Zabona
meaning: Yolqinli, ravshan, nurli qiz

name: Zavra, Zavraxon
meaning: Qar. Zahro, Zahroxon yoki Zuhra, Zuhraxon

name: Zavqiya
meaning: Xursand, shodon, baxtiyor qiz

name: Zadagul
meaning: Hadeb qiz tug‘ilaverishidan zada bo‘lib berilgan ism

name: Zaima
meaning: Boshliq, sarvar bo‘luvchi, rahnamolik qiluvchi qiz

name: Zaynab
meaning: To‘liqdan kelgan, semiz; kelishgan, go‘zal. Zaynab nomi Muhammad (sav) qizining ismi bo‘lgan

name: Zaynabbeka
meaning: Qar. Zaynab (Zaynab+beka)

name: Zaynabbonu
meaning: Go‘zal va yuksak martabali, muhtarama qiz

name: Zaynabgul
meaning: Guldek ko‘rkam, kelishgan qiz

name: Zaynigul
meaning: Gulga burkangan nafosat, guldek ko‘rkam qiz

name: Zayniya
meaning: Bezangan, arolangan qiz

name: Zaynura
meaning: Go‘zal, zebo qiz

name: Zaytuna
meaning: Hayoti zaytun daraxtidek doimo yashnab, gullab tursin yoki zaytundek mahkam, mustahkam bo‘lsin

name: Zaytungul
meaning: Zaytun gulidek zebo qiz

name: Zakiya, Zakiyaxon
meaning: Ziyrak, sezgir, tezfahm qiz

name: Zalifa
meaning: Jingalak sochli qiz yoki tirishqoq, g‘ayratli qiz

name: Zaliqa
meaning: So‘zamol, go‘zal nutq sohibi, notiq

name: Zamzam
meaning: Makka shahrida Ka’ba yaqinidagi buloq, muqaddas suv. Umri Zamzamdek boqiy va zilol bo‘lsin

name: Zamzambeka
meaning: Zamzamdek tiniq, pokiza va beklar naslidan bo‘lgan qiz

name: Zamzamgul
meaning: Zamzam suvidek tiniq, pokiza hamda guldek zebo qiz

name: Zamzamxon
meaning: Qar. Zamzam (Zamzam+xon)

name: Zamina
meaning: Ona yer (ona zamin) farzandi

name: Zamira
meaning: Olijanob, vijdonli, pokdomon qiz

name: Zamirxon
meaning: Qar. Zamir (Zamir+xon)

name: Zamona
meaning: Davrining, zamonining munosib qizi

name: Zamongul
meaning: Davrining guldek suluv qizi

name: Zamonqiz
meaning: Davr, zamon qizi

name: Zangor
meaning: Yuqori, ulug‘ martabali qiz yoki ko‘zlari ko‘k, ko‘k kozli qiz

name: Zanjira
meaning: Ziynatli, bezangan, ko‘rkam yoki zanjirdek mahkam, mustahkam

name: Zarangul
meaning: Zarang daraxti gulidek ko‘rkam, mustahkam qiz. Eht.: Zaranduz ismining qisqargan shakli

name: Zarangduz
meaning: Zarlangan, zar, tilladek yarqiroq, ko‘rkam, go‘zal

name: Zaranqiz
meaning: Zaran darxtidek mahkam, mustahkam.. Eht.: Zaranduz

name: Zarafshon
meaning: Zar sochuvchi, oltinli; nurli, nurafshon

name: Zarbegim
meaning: Oltin, zardek qimmatli, qadrli va beklar nasliga mansuv qiz

name: Zarbibi
meaning: Qadrli, qimmatli, bebaho qiz, tillo qiz

name: Zarbonu
meaning: Tiilo qiz, oltin sochli qiz

name: Zarbof
meaning: Zabofdek chiroyli, ko‘rkam, boy-badavlat, martabali

name: Zarbuvi
meaning: Tillo qiz

name: Zarbuvish
meaning: Qar. Zarbuvi

name: Zargul

meaning: Qulog‘i kemtik yoki burishiq bo‘lib yohud qulog‘I kichkina bo‘lin tugilgan bola

name: Chinpo‘lat
meaning: Haqiqiy, sof po‘latdek mustahkam bola yoki umri to‘liq qilib berilgan po‘latdek mustahkam bola

name: Chintemir
meaning: Umri to‘liq qilib berilgan temirdek mustahkam bola

name: Chinterak
meaning: To‘g‘ri o‘sgan terak

name: Chintoy
meaning: Umri to‘liq, rost qilib berilgan suyukli, erkatoy bola

name: Chinturdi
meaning: Umrini to‘liq qilib berilgan o‘g‘il yashasin, umri uzoq bo‘lsin

name: Chintursin
meaning: Umri to‘liq qilib berilgan bola tursin, yashasin

name: Chinxo‘ja
meaning: Umri rost, to‘liq qilib berilgan xo‘jalar avlodiga mansub bola

name: Chincha
meaning: Umri uzoq kenja, jajji bola

name: Chinqora
meaning: Umrini to‘liq qilib berilgan kuchli, qudratli bola

name: Chinqul
meaning: Allohning umri uzoq bandasi

name: Chirmash
meaning: Oiladagilarga yaqinlashgin, bog‘lanib, chirmashib olgin, ya’ni sog‘ bo‘lsin. Shakllari: Chirmashboy, Chirmashxon

name: Chiroq
meaning: Hayoti yorug‘, nurli bo‘lsin yoki orzu qilingan bola

name: Chirog‘ali
meaning: Alining iltifoti, nuri tufayli topilgan bola

name: Chitboy
meaning: Nozik tabiat, tabiatli bola

name: Chig‘atoy
meaning: Aynan: Bola yoki jasur, botir, nomuschan. Bu nom Chingizxonning ikkinchi o‘g‘il ismi bo‘lgan

name: Chovdir, Chovdur
meaning: Aynan: Ovoza, ya’ni mashhur, taniqli yoki chovdir (turkman urug‘i)lar orasida tug‘ilgan

name: Chodir
meaning: Kapada tug‘ilgan bola yoki pardali bo‘lib tug‘ilgan bola. Sol: Pardaboy

name: Chokar
meaning: Xizmatkor; navkar yoki yovvosh, odobli, mo‘min-qobil

name: Cholboy
meaning: Buvasining nomi berilgan bola yoki burul ot (ko‘kish, xoldor ot) dek baquvvat bo‘lsin yohud tukli bo‘lib tug‘ilgan bola

name: Choparboy
meaning: Ulg‘ayib chopqillab yursin yoki yaxshi daraklar keltiruvchi, qutli bola bo‘lsin

name: Chor, Chorboy
meaning: Oiladagi to‘rtinchi o‘g‘il (farzand) yoki kirli, iflos, yomon bola. Keyingi ma’noda ism bolani yomon ko‘zlardan asrash niyatida qoyiladi. Shakllari: Chorboy, Chortoy

name: Chori
meaning: Oiladagi to‘rtinchi farzand yoki Choriyor ismining shakli

name: Choriyor
meaning: Aynan: To‘rt do‘st, maslakdosh. Bular xalifai barhaqlar (choriyorlar) Abu Bakr Siddiq, Umar, Usmon, Alilardir

name: Chorikeldi
meaning: Alloh ato qilgan to‘rtinchi o‘g‘il

name: Chorimirza
meaning: To‘rtinchi o‘g‘il ulg‘ayib mirzalardek bilimdon yigit bolsin

name: Chorixo‘ja
meaning: Xo‘jalar avlodiga mansub bo‘lgan to‘rtinchi o‘gil

name: Choriqul
meaning: Qar. Chori (Chori+qul)

name: Choriqurbon
meaning: Qurbon oyida tug‘ilgan to‘rtinchi bola

name: Chormuhammad
meaning: Qar. Chor va Muhammad

name: Chortoq, Chortoqboy
meaning: Chortoqda tug‘ilgan bola

name: Chorshanba
meaning: Chorshanba kuni tug‘ilgan bola

name: Chorshanboy
meaning: Qar. Chorshanba

name: Chunon
meaning: Intiq bo‘lib kutilgan bola. Shakllari: Chunonbek, Chunonboy, Chunontoy, Chunonqul

name: Chunonmirza
meaning: Intiq bo‘lib kutilgan o‘g‘il ulg‘ayib mirzolardek yigit bolsin

name: Chust
meaning: Aynan: Chaqqon, shay, mohir, zebo qiz mahkam, mustahkam yohud munosib, sazovor. Eht.: Chustda tug‘ilgan bola, Chust farzandi

name: Chuchuk
meaning: Shirin, yoqimtoy; aziz, e’zozli

name: Cho‘yon
meaning: Qar. Cho‘yan

name: Cho‘kish
meaning: Cho‘kich (cho‘kish)dek mustahkam bola

name: Cho‘lbosh
meaning: Cho‘lda tavallud topgan to‘ng‘ich bola

name: Cho‘limurod
meaning: Cho‘lda tug‘ilgan bola ulg‘ayib murod-maqsadiga yetsin yoki cho‘lda erishilgan orzu, tilak

name: Cho‘liq
meaning: Cho‘ponning yordamchisi, kichik cho‘pn

name: Cho‘lli, Cho‘lliboy
meaning: Cho‘lda tug‘ilgan bola

name: Cho‘lmurod
meaning: Cho‘lda tug‘ilgan o‘g‘il sog ulgayib murod-maqsadiga yetsin yoki cholda erishilgan orzu, tilak

name: Cho‘lpon
meaning: Tong yulduzi, yorug‘ yulduz (Venera), ya’ni tolei baland, saodatli bola

name: Cho‘lponqul
meaning: Allohning tolei baland, saodatli bandasi, quli

name: Cho‘ponqul
meaning: Sog‘ ulg‘ayib qo‘ychi, qo‘ychivon bolsin; mollari kop, boy-badavlat bolsin yoki bechora, xoksor bola. Keyingi ma’noda ism bolani yomon kozlardan asrashga qaratilgan

name: Cho‘rtanboy
meaning: Cho‘rtan baliqdek erkin, yashovchan bo‘lsin

name: Cho‘tboy
meaning: Tesha, cho‘tdek mustahkam bola yoki kindigi cho‘t (tesha) bilan kesilgan bola

name: Cho‘tir
meaning: Cho‘tir, ya’ni xunuk bola. Bolani yomon ko‘zlardan asrash uchun qo‘yiladigan ism

name: Cho‘tmamat
meaning: Qar. Cho‘tmuhammad

name: Cho‘tmat
meaning: Qar. Cho‘tmuhammad

name: Cho‘tmuhammad
meaning: Cho‘t (tesha) dek mustahkam o‘g‘ilni Muhammad (sav) o‘z panohida asrasin

name: Cho‘tpo‘lat
meaning: Cho‘t (tesha) va po‘latdek mustahkam bola

name: Cho‘yan, Cho‘yanboy
meaning: Cho‘yandek mustahkam bo‘lsin

name: Cho‘yanbek
meaning: Beklar avlodiga mansub bo‘lgan cho‘yandek mustahkam bola

name: Cho‘yanturdi
meaning: Cho‘yandek mustahkam bo‘lib turadigan, ya’ni yashab ketadigan bola

name: Cho‘yanqul
meaning: Allohnig cho‘yandek mustahkam bandasi, quli

name: Cho‘qmor
meaning: To‘qmoq (cho‘qmor) deb mustahkam va zabardast bo‘lsin

name: Cho‘qqi
meaning: Hayoti qoya (cho‘qqi)dek yuksak bo‘lsin

name: Cho‘g‘olboy
meaning: Baquvvat, kuchli, mahkam, mustahkam bola

name: Chaman
meaning: Hayoti, gulzor, o‘tloqdek yashnoq bo‘lsin yoki ko‘rkam, zebo qiz yohud chamand - o‘jar, qaysar bola. Shakllari: Chamanbibi, Chamangul, Chamanoy, Chamanxon

name: Chamanbibi
meaning: Hayoti chamandek yashnagan, baxtiyor bola

name: Chamanbuvi
meaning: Go‘zal, sohibjamol qiz

name: Chamanqul
meaning: Gullar chamanidek zebo qiz, chamanzordek yashnoq, go‘zal qiz

name: Charos
meaning: Katta qora ko‘zli qiz, ko‘zlari charosdek chiroyli qiz

name: Charosxon
meaning: Katta qora ko‘zli qiz, ko‘zlari charosdek chiroyli qiz

name: Chashma
meaning: Hayoti buloq suvidek mustafo hamda davomli bo‘lsin. Shakllari: Chashmagul, Chashmaxon

name: Chag‘ona
meaning: Xushovoz, shirinyil, xushkalom; yoqimtoy dilkash qiz

name: Chevar, Chevarxon
meaning: Mohir to‘quvchi yoki to‘quvchi; qo‘li gul qiz

name: Chervon, Chervonoy
meaning: Qimmatli, aziz, topilmas, noyob

name: Chechak
meaning: Gul, maysa; go‘zal, zebo, sohibjamol. Shakllari: Chechakgul, Chechakoy

name: Chechakoy
meaning: Guldek zebo va oydek suluv qiz

name: Chehra
meaning: Yuz, jamol, ko‘rk; asli: Gulchehra (qar.)

name: Chehragul
meaning: Gulyuzli; chiroyli, go‘zla qiz

name: Chehrashod
meaning: Yuzlari kulib turgan qiz; shodon, baxtiyor

name: Chilla
meaning: Chilla payti (40 kunlik issiq yoki sovuq) da tug‘ilgan bola yoki chilla - kamon ipidek mahkam, mustahkam bola. Shakllari: Chillaxon

name: Chimbuvi
meaning: Chim (ajriqzor) dek mahkam; to‘silgan, himoyaga olingan qiz

name: Chimil, Chimilxon
meaning: Eht.: Chimil  -  chimir - pishiq, puxta; bosiq, vazmin

name: Chimmatoy
meaning: Berkilgan, yashirilgan, himoyalangan, daxlsiz qiz

name: Chindaxol
meaning: Bog‘langan, turmaklangan, mahkamlangan va xoldor qiz

name: Chindi
meaning: Jingalak, turmaklangan sochli qiz

name: Chinjamol
meaning: Chiroyli, sohibjamol qiz

name: Chinnibahor
meaning: Qar. Chinni va Bahor

name: Chinniposhsha
meaning: Chinniguldek zebo va baland martabali qiz

name: Chinnixol
meaning: Quloqlari kichkina bo‘lib yoki jingalak sochli bo‘lib tug‘ilgan bola

name: Chinora
meaning: Chinordek umri uzoq qiz

name: Chinorbibi
meaning: Umri chinordek uzoq bo‘lsin

name: Chinorgul
meaning: Chinor kabi uzoq umrli va guldek go‘zal qiz

name: Chinsuluv
meaning: Jingalak sochli yoki umrini to‘liq, rost qilib berilgan go‘zal qiz

name: Chirbonu
meaning: g‘olib, muzaffar, bahodir, pahlavon

name: Chirvon
meaning: Qar. Chirbonu

name: Chirmal
meaning: Oiladagilarga chirmashib, bog‘lanib qolsin, o‘lmasin. Sol: Chirmash

name: Chiroy
meaning: Go‘zallik, ko‘rkamlik, go‘zal chehrali, sohibjamol

name: Chiroygul
meaning: Go‘zal chehrali qiz, sohibkamol, gulyuzli qiz

name: Chiroyxol
meaning: Xol bilan tug‘ilgan go‘zalm sohibjamol qiz

name: Choygul
meaning: Choyning gulidek go‘zal, yoqimli qiz. Eht.: Chiroygul (qar.) ismining eq.shakli

name: Chorgul
meaning: Oiladagi to‘rtinchi qiz yoki nopok, yomon qiz. Keyingi ma’no chaqaloqni yomon ko‘zdan asrash niyatini ifodalaydi

name: Chorshanbu, Chorshanbuvi
meaning: Chorshanba kuni tug‘ilgan bola

name: Chuchukgul
meaning: Shirin, yoqimtoy va guldek go‘zal qiz

name: Chuchukoy
meaning: Shirin, yoqimtoy va oydek suluv qiz

name: Chuchukxon
meaning: Qar. Chuchuk (Chuchuk+xon)

name: Cho‘lbibi
meaning: Dashtda (cho‘lda) tug‘ilgan baland martabali qiz yoki mushtoq bo‘lib yurib erishilgan qiz

name: Cho‘lponbu
meaning: Iqboli baland yoki tong yulduzi Cho‘lpondek nurli, go‘zal qiz

name: Cho‘lponoy
meaning: Tong yulduzi Cho‘lpon va oydek go‘zal qiz yoki oydek suluv, iqboli baland qiz

name: Cho‘lponxon
meaning: Cho‘lpon yulduzidek go‘zal va baland martabali, e’zozli qiz

name: Cho‘ri
meaning: Qul, xizmatkori qiz

name: Cho‘ribibi
meaning: Qar. Cho‘ri (Cho‘ri+bibi)
